@startuml
title Sueca - Sequencia: Perfil e Replay (Estado Atual)

actor "Jogador" as User
participant "ProfilePage" as ProfileUI
participant "ReplayListPage" as ReplayListUI
participant "ReplayPlayerPage" as ReplayPlayerUI
participant "ProfileController" as ProfileCtrl
participant "ReplayListController" as ListCtrl
participant "ReplayPlayerController" as PlayerCtrl
participant "ProfileRepository" as ProfileRepo
participant "ReplayRepository" as ReplayRepo
participant "ProfileRemoteDataSource" as ProfileDS
participant "ReplayRemoteDataSource" as ReplayDS
participant "GraphqlService" as GQLClient
participant "GraphQL API" as GQL
participant "GameResolver.Events" as EventsResolver
participant "EventService" as EventSvc
participant "EventRepository" as EventRepo

== 1) Abrir perfil ==
User -> ProfileUI : abrir perfil
ProfileUI -> ProfileCtrl : loadProfile()
ProfileCtrl -> ProfileRepo : fetchProfile(userId)
ProfileRepo -> ProfileDS : fetchProfile(userId)
ProfileDS -> GQLClient : query user + userStats
GQLClient -> GQL : GraphQL request
GQL --> GQLClient : user, userStats
GQLClient --> ProfileDS : payload
ProfileDS --> ProfileRepo : Profile
ProfileRepo --> ProfileCtrl : Profile
ProfileCtrl --> ProfileUI : render perfil

== 2) Abrir historico ==
User -> ProfileUI : clicar "Historico de Jogos"
ProfileUI -> ReplayListUI : navegar
ReplayListUI -> ListCtrl : loadGames()
ListCtrl -> ReplayRepo : fetchUserGames(userId)
ReplayRepo -> ReplayDS : fetchUserGames(userId)
ReplayDS -> GQLClient : query userGames (metadata)
GQLClient -> GQL : GraphQL request
GQL --> GQLClient : games (id, roomId, players, createdAt)
GQLClient --> ReplayDS : payload
ReplayDS --> ReplayRepo : List<GameSummary>
ReplayRepo --> ListCtrl : lista
ListCtrl --> ReplayListUI : render jogos

== 3) Abrir replay de um jogo ==
User -> ReplayListUI : selecionar jogo
ReplayListUI -> ReplayPlayerUI : navegar
ReplayPlayerUI -> PlayerCtrl : load()
PlayerCtrl -> ReplayRepo : fetchGameReplay(userId, gameId)
ReplayRepo -> ReplayDS : fetchGameReplay(...)
ReplayDS -> GQLClient : query userGames + events
GQLClient -> GQL : GraphQL request

loop para cada game.events
  GQL -> EventsResolver : resolver field events(gameId)
  EventsResolver -> EventSvc : GetEventsByGameID(gameId)
  EventSvc -> EventRepo : FindByGameID(gameId)
  EventRepo --> EventSvc : events ordenados
  EventSvc --> EventsResolver : events
end

GQL --> GQLClient : jogo + eventos
GQLClient --> ReplayDS : payload
ReplayDS --> ReplayRepo : GameSummary(events)
ReplayRepo --> PlayerCtrl : replay completo
PlayerCtrl -> PlayerCtrl : build frames locais
PlayerCtrl --> ReplayPlayerUI : timeline pronta

== 4) Playback ==
User -> ReplayPlayerUI : play/pause/seek
ReplayPlayerUI -> PlayerCtrl : play()/pause()/seekTo()
PlayerCtrl -> PlayerCtrl : avanca indice e frame local
PlayerCtrl --> ReplayPlayerUI : atualiza mesa e eventos

@enduml
